    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The easiest solution I found was to download and install Visual Studio Code Insiders.  It's nearly identical except that it's known to lag less.  Installing this will also clear any extensions or preferences you have enabled which might be causing the lag:</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/insiders/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://code.visualstudio.com/insiders/</a></p>\n\n<p>You may also need to run it from the command line with the --disable-gpu flag</p>\n\n<pre><code>code-insiders --disable-gpu\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>/Applications/Visual\\ Studio\\ Code\\ -\\ Insiders.app/Contents/MacOS/Electron --disable-gpu\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>depending on your OS</p>\n"
  }, {
