    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I've now had this problem a number of times. As a matter of fact I just had it right now.\nWhat solves it for me is to</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Close VS code</li>\n<li>Unpin it from my taskbar</li>\n<li>Pin it back</li>\n</ol>\n<p>It works well after that.</p>\n<p>Closing and reopening VS Code has never worked for me</p>\n"
