    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h2>Please disable <code>Spring Boot Tools</code> from Pivotal!!!</h2>\n<p>This extension doesn't work well with other Java extesions.(ie. Extesion pack for Java and Language support for Java)</p>\n<p>After disabling it, I've seen significant speed increase with Intellisense, and CPU load reduced as a result. Please get rid of the thing!!!</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 22739480,
      "reputation" : 365,
      "user_id" : 16901221,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/f144c92e77b6ffde0ce7f126f765b097?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
