    "answer_id" : 76061633,
    "question_id" : 48961795,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>for me, it was Language pack extension issue,</p>\n<p>when i uninstall Language pack for my country, it resolved.</p>\n<p>(updated)</p>\n<p>try disable hardware acceleration</p>\n<p>Disable hardware acceleration: VS Code uses hardware acceleration to improve performance, but it can sometimes cause issues with typing lag. To disable hardware acceleration, go to File &gt; Preferences &gt; Settings, search for &quot;hardware acceleration&quot; and uncheck the box.</p>\n<p>thanks to GPT</p>\n"
